name: Frostfang Iridian Wyvern
text: Beneath the auroras, Frostfang shimmered, its iridescent fur and icy wings undulating with magic. Villagers whispered legends of the winged protector in the frozen heavens. Each night, its fangs glinted above, a spectral guardian warding off darkness—a celestial beast woven from the tapestry of dreams and winter's breath.
